# ⚙️ Jenkins CI/CD Module ⚙️

---

**⚒️ Tools and Concepts Covered ⚒️**
- Jenkins installation and configuration (WAR & package-based)
- Jenkins Web UI overview and security setup
- Freestyle projects and Pipeline jobs
- Webhooks with GitHub
- Integrating Git, GitHub, Maven, Docker
- Plugins: GitHub, Docker, Pipeline, Email, etc.
- Jenkins agents and distributed builds

---

**💻 Hands-on Activities 💻**
- Installed Jenkins on Ubuntu VM and accessed it on port 8080
- Installed and configured required plugins
- Created and ran Freestyle job to clone and build Maven project from GitHub
- Configured pipeline job using `Jenkinsfile`
- Integrated Jenkins with Docker to build and push Docker images automatically
- Triggered CI pipeline using GitHub webhook
- Deployed Docker containers to dev/prod manually via post-build steps

---

**🧠 Key Learnings 🧠**
- Real-world CI/CD workflow using Jenkins
- Understanding build triggers and post-build actions
- Writing and debugging Jenkinsfiles (Scripted and Declarative)
- Automating end-to-end pipeline from code push to deployment
- Securing Jenkins and managing users/roles
